title: Coconut Rice
ingredients: 2 cups rice|1 cup coconut milk|1 tsp salt|2 tbsp cooking oil

title: Garlic Chicken Curry
ingredients: 1 kg chicken|4 garlic cloves|2 tbsp curry powder|1 cup coconut milk|salt to taste

title: Spicy Lentil Soup
ingredients: 1 cup lentils|1 onion|2 green chili|1/4 tsp turmeric|water as needed
